data.description: AMAZING!! This STUNNING Home Features an Astonishing Open Floor Plan that Boasts Pride of Ownership Throughout!! Packed with Approx. 1,750 sqft of “NEWER” this Beauty Opens up to a HUGE Kitchen with Loads of Cabinet Space, 2021 Stainless Steel Appliances, 2021 Granite Countertops, 2021 Custom Subway Tiled Backsplash, Followed by a 2021 Roof, 2023 HVAC System, 2021 Hot Water Heater, THREE Full Bathrooms, NEWER Windows, and Recessed Lighting. This Home is Designed for Entertaining! The HUGE Private Backyard Oasis Offers Plenty of Room to Host Family Friendly Gatherings...BBQ’s...Soccer... and Football Games!! Updated, Turn-Key, and LOADED with Gorgeousness!! Conveniently Located Near Interstates, Shipyard, Portsmouth Medical Center, Shopping, Restaurants, Schools, and a Short Ferry Ride to Trendy Waterside!! Welcome Home!
